    <p>With 3-6 Scatter symbols, you can hit the jackpot with up to 20 free spins, and indulge in one of three modifiers that would make Rudolph jealous. Hotel Yeti Way serves up plenty of wintry fun that will make you forget your winter doldrums. Who needs a ski trip when you can get Yeti-fied right from your own couch?</p>"
