{
    "headline": "<h2>Gameplay and Special Features</h2>",
    "content": "<p>Get ready to hit the jackpot with Hotel Yeti Way! With a 6x4 reel structure and up to a whopping 4,096 ways to win, your chances of taking home big wins are higher than ever. Plus, the game offers the possibility of expanding to 262,144 active ways to win - it's like hitting the lottery, but without having to leave the comfort of your own home!</p> 

