    <p>Feeling lucky? The Scatter symbol can give up to 20 free spins with three modifiers available. That's right, you could be spinning into a frenzy with even more chances to win big. Also, the multiplier reel is present to boost your winnings - because in Hotel Yeti Way, the only thing better than winning is winning MORE.</p>"
}

